; Status messages
;
MSG_STATUS_ERROR_TRANSFER_SOCKET (//)
STATUS: Error on transfer socket
;
MSG_STATUS_TIMEOUT_RECV (//)
STATUS: Closing transfer socket, data timeout, no more data was received in a timely fashion
;
MSG_STATUS_TIMEOUT_SEND (//)
STATUS: Closing transfer socket, data timeout, no more data was sent in a timely fashion
;
