STATUS: I SHOULD NOT BE HERE!
;
MSG_STATUS_REMOTE_CLOSED (//)
STATUS: Remote closed transfer socket
;
MSG_STATUS_CLOSED_CONTROL (//)
STATUS: closed control connection
;
MSG_STATUS_CANT_SEND (//)
STATUS: cannot send command, waiting for ftp response to previous command
;
MSG_STATUS_CANT_SEND_NOT_CONNECTED (//)
STATUS: cannot send command, not connected
;
MSG_STATUS_CANT_SEND_SELECT_FAILED (//)
STATUS: cannot send command, select() failed
;
